snippet.textDisplay:
Ustaad - the grandmaster i.e. definitely Ustaad Raees Khan was the grandmaster of Sitar. His rank is in the same list as of Beethoven or Mozart in playing piano. No doubt he was the greatest Sitar player of South Asia whose replacement is not possible.

When he picked the strings, the Sitar delivered the sensational music itself.

He will be remembered among the hearts of true Sufism lovers.

snippet.textDisplay:
One of the greatest artists this universe had just once… Ustad
Salamat Ali Khan, Raushan Ara Begum, Ustad Nasrat Fateh Ali Khan, Farruakh
Fateh Ali Khan, Ghulam Ali (Ghazal), Mehdi Hassan, Ustad Raees Khan, these all
are pearls of one string. I bet none of these will come twice, never! 

We are blessed that have a jewel like Ustad Raees Khan
living among us. He belongs to same monarch tribe…monarch of the art and
perfection!  Legendary!
